                            <comment id="54937" author="adilger" created="Wed, 27 Mar 2013 17:34:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just to chime in - I&apos;ve also found this debug code to be problematic, and would prefer that it be simplified in some manner. IIRC, my complaint was about the size of buffer it allocated, but in any case it is messy. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
